text: During CNY eve, the food delivery was significantly delayed, and the service fell short of expectations. Waited for 2 hours but only 3/8 of the food were delivered. Highly disappointed!

Waited very long during CNY Eve, more than 1.5hrs.
Food were cold or room temp when served.
The current promo $49.90 set menu for 3-4 pax is good and value-for-money. For more pax, option to choose the $99.90 set menu or order from the extensive ala carte menu.
